verbose_text: Fluorescent cells were FAC sorted separately for LC-MS/MS peptidomic analysis (XREF_FIG F), confirming that they contained high and enriched levels of gut hormones from proglucagon (GCG), PYY, PPY, and NTS, as well as detectable levels of UCN3 and several secretogranin / chromogranin derived peptides.
evidence: levels of gut hormones from proglucagon
